{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d0b589549","title":"消灭关上之敌的部署","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"261f1d9d37","index":0,"year":1936,"month":3,"day":5,"articleId":"4d0b589549"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"066757f213","type":"paragraph","text":"消灭关上之敌的部署！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4d0b589549"},{"id":"c16da6211a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年3月5日）林、楚，徐、程：甲、关上以北之敌已进至土虎圩，川口之敌已进至上下李村乙、着红军第十五军团全部本日集中水头待命，派小部队向上下李村游击。丙、着红军第一军团一、四两师，本日集中关上东端距关上二十里或三十里地区。二师主力集中关上附近，一部阻带敌于方年包附近。丁、两军团均准备六号或九号回合消灭该敌。红军第十五军团不应尚上下季村前进","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4d0b589549"},{"id":"c9fb3118c6","type":"paragraph","text":"彭毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4d0b589549"},{"id":"5b2c2b97a5","type":"paragraph","text":"五日二时11]这是毛泽东和红军第一方面军司令员彭德怀给第一方而军第一军团军团长林题、政治委员楚荣臻和第十五军团军团长徐海东、政治变员程子华的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4d0b589549"}],"page":{"id":"f110ad34dc","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4d0b589549","start":308,"end":308}}}},"__N_SSG":true}